Package: ontoFAST
Type: Package
Title: Interactive and semi-automatic annotation of characters with biological ontologies 
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Sergei Tarasov
Maintainer: Sergei Tarasov <sergei.tarasov@helsinki.fi>
Description: The package provides convenient tools for annotating characters or character matrices, used in phylogenetics, with anatomy ontologies. It also provides functions for simple queuing of characters using ontological relationships. The main aim of this package is to stimulate integration of comparative phylogenetics and ontological approaches.
URL: https://github.com/sergeitarasov/ontoFAST
